    "permit_type": "Early AssistancePC - PreApplication Conference",
    "work_description": "A Pre-Application Conference to discuss access alternatives for an existing powerline corridor. The powerline corridor currently lacks reliable access for power pole and line maintenance needs. In the near term, PGE proposes to develop a permanent access to replace a power pole along Marquam Trail, and for the long term, establish access to maintain poles and their associated transmission lines following adverse weather events. Two access route alternatives are under consideration.",
